  <header>
    <h1>Spaghetti Bolognese</h1>
    <p>A classic Italian pasta dish that's perfect for dinner!</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <figure>
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x250.png?text=Spaghetti+Bolognese" alt="A plate of Spaghetti Bolognese">
      <figcaption>Delicious homemade spaghetti bolognese</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>200g spaghetti</li>
      <li>2 tbsp olive oil</li>
      <li>1 onion, chopped</li>
      <li>2 garlic cloves, minced</li>
      <li>400g minced beef</li>
      <li>400g canned tomatoes</li>
      <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
      <li>Grated parmesan (optional)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Boil the spaghetti according to package instructions.</li>
      <li>Heat olive oil in a pan and saut√© onion and garlic.</li>
      <li>Add minced beef and cook until browned.</li>
      <li>Stir in canned tomatoes and simmer for 15 minutes.</li>
      <li>Season with salt and pepper.</li>
      <li>Drain spaghetti and mix with the sauce.</li>
      <li>Serve with grated parmesan on top.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Cooking Time</h2>
    <table border="1">
      <tr>
        <th>Prep Time</th>
        <th>Cook Time</th>
        <th>Total Time</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>10 minutes</td>
        <td>20 minutes</td>
        <td>30 minutes</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </section>

